    "body": "FYI:\r\n\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n  \"method\": \"debug_traceCall\",\r\n  \"id\": 67,\r\n  \"params\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"from\": \"0x0C46dADBc6271511F25273cE856eCF799022dA63\",\r\n      \"to\": \"0x7a250d5630B4cF539739dF2C5dAcb4c659F2488D\",\r\n      \"value\": \"0x1BC16D674EC80000\",\r\n      \"data\": \"\",\r\n      \"gas\": \"0x47CED\",\r\n       \"gasPrice\": \"0xf3f0fd31a0\"\r\n    },\r\n    \"latest\",\r\n    {\r\n      \"timeout\": \"120s\",\r\n      \"tracer\": \"callTracer\",\r\n      \"tracerConfig\": {\r\n        \"withLog\": true\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  \r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
