    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "As @jsvisa pointed out, [`eth_estimateGas`](https://ethereum.org/en/developers/docs/apis/json-rpc/#eth_estimategas) will return the error message if your contract fail to execute with the parameters provided. \r\n\r\n`eth_traceCall` can provide more information, but more or less for debugging propose. I think `eth_estimateGas` should be enough for you.",
